Package application.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AmmoModel
    Model for the ammo bunker and the player's ammo.
    CityModel
    Represents the city sprites.
    GameModel
    Represents main game.
    PlayerGunModel
    Represents the gun player uses to fire at the enemey.
    PlayerProjectileModel
    Defines the player's projectiles, creates the blast at the end of the missile's flight, and handles the sprite rotation based on flight path.
    ProjectileModel
    Defines the enemy projectiles, creates the blast when city or ground is hit, and handles the sprite rotation based on flight path.
    ProjectileWave
    Handles the generation of enemy waves and targets them to a city location or player's gun.
    SpriteModel
    Generic sprite model implementing motion, rendering, and boundary checking.
